snippet.title: TWEWY: Noise Busters Update 0.9.1.X
snippet.description:
New Movement based on feedback, New Pins and a new Pin management system.  There shouldn't be many (if any) more big changes to the current systems in the future.

Play It Here: 
http://gamejolt.com/games/arcade/the-world-ends-with-you-noise-busters/60977/

A Score-Attack arcade game based on the cult classic, The World Ends With You.
============================================
http://icugigasoft.freeforums.org/ (Forums)
http://udivision.blogspot.com (Blog)

Note: This is just a free fan game.  Square Enix owns "The World Ends With You", and all related properties.
